room_title: Escape room "The Alchemist" by Spymaker Escape Rooms in Flint
room_description:
It is the middle of the 16th century…The legend says that the Alchemist was searching for the greatest secret of all time; how to transform metal into gold.  This is how the Philosopher’s Stone was created. You have to find the stone in his dangerous laboratory and keep it out of his greedy hands!
Dive into the magic and mysterious in the mystical medieval age. Find the Philosopher’s stone in 60 minutes or be fed to his dragons!
